Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:03.96,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.70,0:01:11.78,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:18.93,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.23,0:01:25.55,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:33.21,OP,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.09,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril! We need to be stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.72,0:02:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, don't look him in the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you won't be able to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.40,0:03:30.20,Series,,0,0,0,,Wounds and Pain
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alti, let's follow those birds! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of a mission right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, who cares about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like the enemy's around, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're only out here because they're paranoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They've been flying for a long time, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far they're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like they've been flying the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.40,0:04:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They rest their wings when they get tired,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have to eat sometime, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like everyone's been really distracted lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.67,0:04:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.05,0:04:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we finally managed to get put back on duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone's still a little out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Aaeru isn't flying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the Sibylla Aurea been doing lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.15,0:04:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't like the feeling of being somehow incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm starting to get used to the others being gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we can't go back to being the old Chor Tempest after all, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama, I've only ever had my eyes on you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along, Limone, we're going to the pool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still small, so you need to build up your stamina—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You come back here this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we all sit down and eat together first?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.63,0:05:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Sibylla Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this... the Sibylla Aurea's?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still being repaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.18,0:06:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had to rebuild her almost from the ground up,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's been hard to get all the parts we've needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wounds still haven't healed, have they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since you've flown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Hey! Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.06,0:06:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of hiding in there all the time, pull yourself together and get out here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you haven't come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Chor Tempest only gets sent on pointless missions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't go on like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't fly if we're stuck in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:07:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, that pig-headed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, what a childish thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.79,0:07:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I'm in no position to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You really didn't need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Aaeru is such a troublesome girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be getting on your nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I make her stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that might require drastic measures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.79,0:08:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's time you made a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you're going to do. Things can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.88,0:08:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to come back to the choir or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you intend to go to the Spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,then this time, I will go with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.14,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether to go to the Spring, or to keep flying the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.07,0:08:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.49,0:08:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize I have to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.36,0:09:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But... whichever choice I make, it feels like it will be a betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A betrayal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Of Amuria?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.18,0:09:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been at your side ever since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've walked beside you all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I can tell you this:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.23,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,you are meant to fly a Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,even if that means betraying Amuria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about it like you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.38,0:10:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She just doesn't give an inch, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you've been so worried about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But why doesn't she try to understand how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand Neviril when she's like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.11,0:11:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about her like you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I do understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she basically just acting like a spoiled child?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.41,0:11:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I know losing Amuria has been hard for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,but she's not the only one who misses her, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.81,0:12:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutting herself away like that is just a big pain for everyone around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I went too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just doing a little cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just leave them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Wait a minute, okay? I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.75,0:12:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it looks like they're starting to sparkle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you have such beautiful nails, you have to take good care of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium-sama will scold you if you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I can do something to help you, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I get to touch you while I do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.16,0:13:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... she's probably lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.55,0:13:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...is probably lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my face give it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.87,0:13:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... I'm lonely, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.42,0:14:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My, isn't it hot in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then shall we go someplace cooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.40,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Still no change from our princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this certainly brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she remind you of anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hardly uncommon for a sibylla to have doubts about flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I reached out to you back then, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Zooooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da! Zoooom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Zooooom! KABOOM! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Still more of you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmpf! I'm not afraid of an attack like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you can hit us, go ahead and try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoooom! Da-da-da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.57,0:15:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Para-sama! Enemy to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire the machine guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're incredible, Para-sama! Not a single miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Da-da-da!  Da-da-da-da-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here come more of them, through the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.25,0:15:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Stingray Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We do this all the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we have to shut it off, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.16,0:16:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaimu-nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We were always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.62,0:17:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I'd stay with her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with her seemed like the most natural thing in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I was conceited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was the only one who could take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the only one who was hurt back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We should stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're still a child, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm not a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.61,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when we try to heal each other's wounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.19,0:18:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,we just end up inflicting more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.20,0:18:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now. Good night, Kaimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you understand, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril! Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen to me for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.82,0:19:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That does it. Stubborn or not, I'm going to drag you out of there myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.54,0:19:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Paraietta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.04,0:19:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.26,0:19:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I get the feeling that talking isn't what you had in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.39,0:19:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Maaju Pool can also be used for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.56,0:19:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So, why do I have to do this with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuria isn't the only reason Neviril is refusing to make a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.55,0:20:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She was thinking about me as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Neviril, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least let me tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't ever felt that you betrayed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.36,0:20:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm grateful that you worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'll entrust you to someone who could be even better for you than Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.82,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.03,0:21:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.25,0:21:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Had enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, you have to become Neviril's pair!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.02,0:22:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to tell {\i1}me{\i0} that!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.53,0:22:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you suppose happens to them after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.28,0:22:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds that rest their wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.16,0:22:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You said they couldn't keep flying forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll start flying again, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.79,0:22:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Flying through the sky is what they're born to do, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.22,0:22:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What they're born to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're just resting their wings, then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.89,0:22:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But a bird that's too badly hurt to fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.94,0:22:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't be able to go on living.
